1.put main.cpp under root path
2.put your depend code under src folder,as this template do,
	you need add CMakeLists.txt to every sub folder,and 
	you can write .txt as this template do
3.you can modify CMakeLists.txt under root path, you can change project name,
	the target name,and you libs name,and so on...
4.after you do the work mentioned, you can run ./build.sh, this script 
	will auto mkdir some folders ,then cmake and make

